<plot>Fearless leader and senseless con, Bounce and his brother, Sugar a crossword puzzle obsessed, half deaf, ex-boxer, try to convince their ex-partner in crime, Vance, aka Bruce, to help them bury a mysterious package in the desert. There's a $75,000 payday waiting if they follow the instructions on the ransom style note. But, Bruce doesn't go along with Bounce's latest scheme easily. This type of behavior doesn't sit well with his wife, Melissa and their new, domesticated, straight-laced life. The contents of the package remain unknown until they reach the burial spot where they decide to take a look. What they find inside changes everything...</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?581146</url></doc>
